| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0320 — Recovery Inhibition (royal)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 69c7ab6c-3567-5bfc-a5da-cdf09ce28f80"
